  <div id="about-lead">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>We think democracy thrives when peopleâ€™s voices are heard. The easier it is for you to reach your member of Congress, the better. It&rsquo;s that simple.</h2>
      <div class="text-center" id="showAbout">
