      <div class="whitebox-container clearfix">
        <div class="row how">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 lead">
            <p>Failure to effectively reach members of Congress has disastrous consequences. Studies shows that politicians <a href="https://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~broockma/broockman_skovron_asymmetric_misperceptions.pdf"> fundamentally misconceive</a> their constituents&rsquo; views, making it harder for them to represent us in the lawmaking process.</p>
            <p>That&rsquo;s why we built democracy.io: a new tool to put you in touch with your members of Congress&mdash;with as few clicks as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
